title: Scorpions - Humanity Hour I (2007)
description:
Humanity: Hour I is a concept album by the German heavy metal band Scorpions, which was released in Europe on May 14, 2007 and in the United States and Canada on August 28, 2007. The leading song "Humanity" was performed by Scorpions on March 24, 2007 at Brussels, Belgium. [Source: Wikipedia]

Genre: Rock
